<HEADLINE>
FT  16 JUL 93 / UK Company News: River &amp; Mercantile shows improvement
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
River &amp; Mercantile Trust reported a net asset value of 183.26p per capital
share as at June 30, against 150.39p at the end of 1992.
