<HEADLINE>
FT  16 JUL 93 / UK Company News: Rentokil offer unconditional
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Rentokil, the environmental and property services group, has declared its
Pounds 75.7m offer for Securiguard unconditional as to acceptances.
By noon yesterday, acceptances had been received for shares representing
40.35 per cent of the security and cleaning company's equity.
Rentokil had already bought 29.7 per cent of Securiguard when it lifted its
