</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Rentokil Group.
    Securiguard Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
