week by the Board of Audit and Inspection of being involved in irregular
deals and bribe-taking.
Under Mr Kim's orders the board investigated recent military hardware
purchases, including a Dollars 5bn air force modernisation plan, which
opposition politicians say were secured through corrupt means.
