<TEXT>
Petrofina, the Belgian oil group, said its wholly-owned Fina Exploration
Minh Hai BV unit would sell a 15 per cent interest in an oil concession
covering three blocks in an offshore area to the south of Vietnam to
Japanese oil companies Cosmo Oil and Japan Petroleum Exploration, Reuter
reports from Brussels.
