scheduled for August.
Fina Exploration Minh Hai is the operator and will retain a 40 per cent
interest in the concession. The other partners are the UK's Enterprise Oil
with 25 per cent and Sodec, a unit of the Royal Dutch/Shell Group, with a 20
per cent stake.
