</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By PETER FRANKLIN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
HEADLAM Group, the floorcoverings and fabrics distribution group, is buying
Claremont Fabrics, a textile converter and fabrics wholesaler.
Consideration is Pounds 5.3m in shares, of which 208,661 are being retained
by one of the vendors and 3.96m are being offered to Headlam shareholders
under a 2-for-13 rights issue at 127p to raise Pounds 5.04m for the vendors.
