<HEADLINE>
FT  15 JUL 93 / People: Departures
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Allan Robertson is retiring from NCR.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>NCR.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
